{
  "stem": "21978.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I wouldn't have expected them to come back, because they've been very, very depressed, I would say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And when I saw the life later, and I saw the old people in Theresienstadt too, I have seen what depression means.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "People didn't really care if they really live or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But young people in Ghetto were having quite chances to lead a culture life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "There were underground theaters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There were singing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "There were people, children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We were not children anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We were adults.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But youngsters were taken to-- not every youngster had the chance-- but from Prague, many of them were put to separate houses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And they had tutors who were teaching them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They had good education.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They have been active in the place, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They have been working on the field in the Theresienstadt, on the-- they were taken sometimes out to work-- some were young people-- out of Theresienstadt to work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I remember only one time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "That must have been some special-- special chance that we had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We have been taken out of Theresienstadt to work on fields to gather the hay.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "It was beautiful there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We have had freedom in the field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "As it was, we have been locked in the-- in the Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I don't know if I am jumping too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Maybe you want to ask questions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for the people who were crowded in the barracks, they were old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were Kaserne-- old barracks for the soldiers-- which were occupied by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Christian people who used to live in that town were sent elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And their houses were taken by-- all by SS or by-- by the guards.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
